::DarkMouse::

She turned and looked at Megatron as he entered the base.
She walked up to Megatron. "I said it showed you intelegence leaving a mouse 
in charge of things.  A mouse I might add who put the defence systems 
together and could defend the base from the main computer console while you 
were away.  I was also telling Scorponok that you had gone to attack the 
Maximal base as you instructed me to do.  But you've returned, and with 
minimal damage.  I did take the liberty of charging up a CR chamber for you 
just case you needed it." She was standing with in a few feet of Megatron.  
She just stood there, she saw the look of anger on his face.  But she wasn't 
afraid anymore.
"Also Quickstrike has yet to return to the base.  If you command me to do 
so, I can try to hale him for you and find out what is going on."
